  <p class="me-3" style="text-align: justify;">
  <b>6.<u class="ms-3">Open Line Communication with 1 CISP.</u></b> The COOPERATIVE shall maintain a close dialogue and communication with 1 CISP on all matters relative to the foregoing with the end in view that services extended shall always be updated, efficient and responsive to the needs of their organization as well as its borrowers.
  </p>

  <p class="me-3" style="text-align: justify;">
  <b>7.<u class="ms-3">Compliance in Good Faith.</u></b> The COOPERATIVE pledges its faithful compliance in good faith of the foregoin agreement and commitment.
  </p>
  
